id":281394,"uid":20696,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T17:18:31.000Z","msg":"其實唔知咁算唔算嗌交，但想搵個地方講下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上星期佢話要應酬同事去聽talk星期日先見<br />\n咁中間就隔左6日無見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁都無野，都無話唔俾佢去，只係半詐營半講笑咁話呢個禮拜唔話你知我做左咩，唔自拍俾你睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後佢就話我狠心，啲對話都係平時大家講笑扮嬲咁。突然間佢就：唉<br />\n之後我問佢做咩，佢：無啦<br />\n嗰下未分到佢係講笑定真係唔開心無即刻氹返佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢就真係燥左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就同佢講sorry，因為佢返緊工唔想同佢嘈費事佢無心機做野，就同佢講唔煩佢喇叫佢俾心機做野。<br />\n然後佢勁晦氣咁講左句：你無煩，係我衰姐<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一齊就半年佢都係第一次咁晦氣咁燥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嗰下我都覺得真係自己太煩，唔應該成日詐營<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">其實雖然得一句，當日就和好如初，但真係好hurt</span></span>"},{"pid":"2e9581a86036dbef2801f534fa01039c0eb69956","tid":281394,"uid":113712,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T18:01:26.000Z","msg":"男朋友成日𥄫女 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e94c7943f56dd127d6a18c68c1807e54b23bbf3","tid":281394,"uid":61917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T18:57:41.000Z","msg":"約左出街但訓著"},{"pid":"8e1572e8df59e504cb9979abe049c38c5f27cc29","tid":281394,"uid":75026,"like":3